        <updateDate>2019-08-20T16:42:20Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Stop Welfare for Any Large Monopoly Amassing Revenue from Taxpayers Act of 2018</b></p> <p>This bill prohibits a large employer from purchasing its own stock if it (1) pays its employees less than $15 an hour, (2) does not provide its employees with specified paid sick leave, or (3) does not comply with a specified compensation ratio with respect to its executive officers and employees. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
